== Bible mhunge kitem :  ==

'''Biblia''' zaun asa Kristanvanchem '''[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bible Povitr Pustok]'''. Taka Povitr Pustok aniek nanv. Haka 2 bhag asat. [[Adlo korar]] ani [[Novo korar]]. Adlea koraran 46 pustokam, zalear novea koraran 27 pustokam asat. Sogllim mellun 73 pustokam Bible-ant melltat.[[File:Holy Bible.JPG|thumb|Povitr Pustok]]


English bhaxentlem,  ‘Bible’, hem utor  ailam ‘ Biblia’   Latin ani ‘Biblos’ Greg bhaxent san. Bible hea utracho  orth asa Pustok (book). ‘Pustok’ hem ek uchit nav kiteak hem pustok soglea lokak, soglea kala passot.  Hea pustoka oxlem dusrem pustok na. Bible, soglea kallantlem vortem khoplolem pustok, billions  copies soglea sonvsarant vanttlolem hem pustok.  Povitr Pustok,  2400 ani zaiteo bhaxen,  bhaxantor kelolem meota.

Bible ant veg veglea vixoi acher pustokam meotai.  Kaideacher pustokam – Levi-Xastr ani Dusri Somurt, Itihas acher pustokam – Ezra ani Dhormdutancho Itihas,  Kovita acher pustokam – Stotram and Upodexok,  Bhovixiovanni – Izaias ani Juanvak Prokasovnni(Revelation), Peleamni boroil'lim jinnye kotha (Biography) – Matev  ani Juanv ani toxim  Potram ‘Epistles’(formal letters) Titak Pauluchem Potr ani Hebrevank Potr.

== Bible boroupi kon ?  ==

Sumar 40  munxeanchem boroilolem   yogdan disun eta  Bible ant.  Povitr Pustok,  laghim  1500 vorsam hea kalant boroilolem disun eta.  Lekhok aslole – Raja, Kharvi, Pujari, Sorkari Odhikari, Xetkar,  Gonvlli ani Dotor. Hea  Soglea vibhinnota modem  ek Ojapacho ekvott dista, ek  mull vixoi guntun hadlolem meota. Bible acho Mull Lekhok -  Dev  and hea karank lagon ho ekvot disti podta.  Bible hem Devachea Svasa vorvim preritt zalam (2 Timothy 3 : 16 ).  Devak  zai aslolem toxem sonvsarachea lekhokani Bible boroilem ani folladik zallem ek poripurnn ani Povitr Devachem Utor (Psalm 12:6; 2 Peter 1:21) Bible hem pustok  don bhagant meota – Ponno Korar ani Novo Korar.  Thodkean, Ponno Korar zaun asa khobor eka ‘Rashtrachi’  ani Novo  Korar zaun asa ek khobor eka ‘Munxeachi’.  ‘Rashtra’ hem  Devachi Yevzonn asloli ‘Munxeak’ – Jezu Christak hea sonvsarant hadpachi.  

Ponnea Korarant, Israel  Rashtrachem stapon  and samball acho vornon meota. Devan  bhasavnni dil’li, Israel rashtra vorvim soglea sonvsarak (Genesis 12:2-3) aplem besanv ghalpachem. Israel rashtra achem stapon zatoch, Devan ek famil vinchli – David achi famil (Psalm 89 : 3-4). ani tea famili vorvim hem besanv soglea sounsarak meopachem.  Davidachea familik ek Munis bhasail’lo jo hem besanv soglea sonvsarak hadpacho. (Isaiah 11 : 1-10)

Novea Korarant,  bhasail’lea Munxeachi yenneachem  vivronn meota ani tea munxeachem nav Jezu.  Jezun,  Adlea Koraracheo bhasavneo  sompurnn keleo ek  purnn jivit jieun, sodvonndar zallo aplea mornan, ani punor jivont  zallo morna uprant.  Jezu zaun asa, Bible hea Povitr Pustok acho sondesh. Jezu fokot munis naslo pun Dev zo munxeachem rup ( kud ani rogot)  gheun amchea modem jielo.  Hea vorvim  kollid amca  korpak tazo mogh  ani taji yevzonn munxea kula sovem. (John 1:14, 14:9). Khoincheam pann ugot kelear Dev amchea sovem uloilolem meota. Bhasavnni - Jezu,  Sorvpodvedar Deva Bapachea uzveak bosla, thuim thaun jiveam ani mel'leanchi mon'subi korunk portun ietolo. 



